# Email sending is currently disabled in this project.
# The contact form now generates a reply message locally.
# If you re-enable email sending later, these are the variables you would use:
# EMAIL_USER=your-email@example.com
# EMAIL_PASS=your-app-password
# EMAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# EMAIL_PORT=465
# EMAIL_SECURE=true
# EMAIL_FROM_NAME=Your Name